summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 17444, entitled, "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley in Block Four (4), University Heights Addition to the City of Seattle, being the alley between Fourteenth Avenue Northeast and Fifteenth Avenue Northeast, from East Fifty-second Street to East Fifty-fifth Street, by grading the same, in accordance with Majority Petition, being File No. 33280, in the office of the City of Seattle of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Payment by Bonds," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
